OL,3,CRetired engineer, 79, raises funds for
OL,4,Ccharity by riding on novelty scooters
OL,6,FHe's something of a local celebrity,
OL,7,Fknown for his quirky inventions - and
OL,8,Fmaking people smile with his
OL,9,Ffundraising.
OL,11,FAnd now Tim Bell from Sheerness, who
OL,12,Fcollects cash while riding on his
OL,13,Fcustomised mobility scooters, is among
OL,14,Fthe nominees for ITV Meridian's Pride
OL,15,Fof Britain Regional Fundraiser of the
OL,16,FYear Award.
OL,18,FTim is a retired engineer. One of his
OL,19,Ffavourite creations - a miniature
OL,20,Freplica of the Kent Surrey and Sussex
OL,21,FAir Ambulance (KSS) helicopter.
