OL,6,FThe 79-year-old designed it over many
OL,7,Fyears and continues to tinker,
OL,8,Frecently adding new LED lights and a
OL,9,Fmusic system.
OL,11,FSo far he has raised more than #56,000
OL,12,Ffor the KSS Air Ambulance.
OL,14,FTim said: "I'm in awe of what they do,
OL,15,Fit's one of the reasons I've stuck
OL,16,Fwith the air ambulance because they're
OL,17,Fsuch lovely people to fundraise for.
OL,18,FThey're so appreciative, it's
OL,19,Fincredible what they do.
