OL,3,CRetired engineer, 79, raises funds for
OL,4,Ccharity by riding on novelty scooters
OL,6,F"And of course, where I live on the
OL,7,FIsle of Sheppey, sometimes it's
OL,8,Fblocked off and they always seem to be
OL,9,Fflying over and landing on Sheppey,
OL,10,Fwhich is one of the reasons I started
OL,11,Ffundraising for them. I wanted to
OL,12,Ffundraise for the whole community.
OL,14,F"Please put money in my bucket,
OL,15,Fbecause you never know, you might need
OL,16,Fthem one day."
OL,18,FBut the miniature air ambulance isn't
OL,19,FTim's only creation.
