OL,3,CRetired engineer, 79, raises funds for
OL,4,Ccharity by riding on novelty scooters
OL,6,FHe has also made a tiny ride-on
OL,7,Freplica of the Sheerness clock tower
OL,8,Fand most recently, he developed a tank
OL,9,F- that fires paper streamers - to
OL,10,Fcelebrate VE Day.
OL,12,FTim regularly dressed up in costumes
OL,13,Fand takes the scooters into his local
OL,14,Ftown centre to collect for charity,
OL,15,Fwhere he is greeted fondly by locals
OL,16,Fand immediately recognised.
OL,18,FHe said: "My philosophy in life is to
OL,19,Fmake people smile and make them feel
OL,20,Fgood.
