OL,6,F"I if I can do that and they can see
OL,7,Fthe amount of effort I've gone to,
OL,8,Fthey might make a donation to the air
OL,9,Fambulance. It's a win win situation.
OL,11,F"To interact with the public is the
OL,12,Fbest part of doing this. You see the
OL,13,Fbest side of the public."
